snippet.title: NHL 21 Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Pre-order NHL 21 Great Eight Edition and get 3 Days Early Access: http://x.ea.com/nhl21/gameplay

In EA SPORTS NHL 21, gameplay has gotten smarter, faster and a whole lot flashier. With innovative moves and massive improvements on both sides of the puck, players have more options than ever before to take control of the game and impose their playstyle on opponents. Recognize Revolutionary with Gameplay in NHL 21. 

NHL 21 officially launches worldwide October 16th. Subscribe for more NHL 21 Trailers: https://bit.ly/3kF5rTK
